{
  "texts": [
    "Upon expressing their consent, the annotators received access to an interface with the task description and instructions, shown in Figure 8.",
    "Along with the instructions, we provided one example for each of the four possible options in the task.",
    "After completing the task, we asked each annotator to describe the properties they considered for comparing the stories.",
    "Specifically, we asked the following question: \"What are the properties of a story that made you select it as being better?\".",
    "Based on the responses and judgements obtained from the annotators (see Section 6), we report qualitative examples in Figures 9, 10, and 11."
  ]
}